{"tid":2185620,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"斯洛伐克總統力挺捷克 稱「不能接受」中國威脅","createTime":"2020-09-02T11:22:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-02T12:18:30.000Z","uid":239336,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"2890a95bfe48bd33de5d1fa6db182f4970928f80","tid":2185620,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T11:22:53.000Z","msg":"中國外長王毅出言恫嚇訪問台灣的捷克參議院議長維特齊一事在歐洲引發憤慨，除了德國外長與歐盟對外事務部之外，斯洛伐克總統卡普托娃（Zuzana Caputova）也表示不能接受中國的威脅。這是歐洲第一次有國家元首出面批評中國對維特齊訪台說三道四。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200902/UXCW4HNUCJFBVPXQUPIXPXVS6Y/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR1kS4fv3EawyMe21ZBudeBtJe0kulEbHHCKfOEj4xfKBzBAyuEuLy_TBCk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200902%2FUXCW4HNUCJFBVPXQUPIXPXVS6Y%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR1kS4fv3EawyMe21ZBudeBtJe0kulEbHHCKfOEj4xfKBzBAyuEuLy_TBCk&d=5n7Vw74FaX2H6oE8X5RxXGqRhi9KU01BjP2Z1UqMPtI%3D&h=12384327\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200902%2FUXCW4HNUCJFBVPXQUPIXPXVS6Y%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR1kS4fv3EawyMe21ZBudeBtJe0kulEbHHCKfOEj4xfKBzBAyuEuLy_TBCk&h=fb47610b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200902/UXCW4HNUCJFBVPXQUPIXPXVS6Y/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR1kS4fv3EawyMe21ZBudeBtJe0kulEbHHCKfOEj4xfKBzBAyuEuLy_TBCk</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p